- Required R packages:
  ```R
  install.packages("remotes")
  remotes::install_github("MRCIEU/TwoSampleMR")  # Core MR analysis
  install.packages("dplyr")                      # Data manipulation
   #other packages are listed in each code.

##The following code were used in this study:
 1. gwas_code.sh: To conduct a sex-stratified and time-stratified GWAS on leisure screen time (LST) from the UK Biobank database with BOLT-LMM linear mixed models.
 2. GCTA_cojo_code.sh: To identify the instrument variables of LST.
 3. Post-GWAS analysis.R: To combine GWAS output data, calculate F statistics and conduct LDSC and pair-wise Z test.
 4. Two-sample-MR analysis of continuous LST exposure.R: To identify causal effect between female LST and five pregnancy-related outcomes.
 5. Two-sample-MR analysis of binary LST exposure.R: To identify causal effect of long LST and short LST on ectopic pregnant.
